Interface CUILogger.ErrorCallback

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErrorCallbackWrapper
    Enclosing class:
    CUILogger

    public static interface CUILogger.ErrorCallback
    Interface for a callback so that clients can receive error events when something goes wrong with the CUILogger.
